      • getDivision

        public int[] getDivision(int index)
        Method return 4 element int table with information about percentage filling maze by elements. Information are prepared for each quarter of maze. It is in table: position 0 - for left bottom q, position 1 - for left top q. position 2 - for right top q, position 3 - for right bottom q.
        Parameters:
        index - Indicate maze to check.
        Returns:
        int[] Table with information about filling for each quarter.
